latestIgtvVideos.title: 12.04.2021 - AARU CAME LIVE WITH @emiway_bantai 🥺
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Okay so what happened was .... 
Emiway sent me a live request but i couldn't join for the first time because there is a certain time limit i guess and then the invitation got expired , i was too sad after that and waited for like 15 minutes or so requesting him to add me again and then he finally did!!!! Oh my god @emiway_bantai you are a sweet heart ❤️ Bantai ki public humesha sath khadi hai . After I ended the live video , i had so much to think over ki ohh shit khatam hue waande ka rap gaana tha sath mein bantai ke , music video ki baat krni thi but trust me uss time pe kuch samajh ni aata like how to respond , what to say and what not to say! My god seriously kuch samajh nahi aata !!!! I was shivering , still can't believe that this actually happened.... I feel grateful and blessed ki 12,000 people mein i was sent a live request by the one the only Emiwayyyy!! I feel so happy or itna ki i couldn't sleep last night and my heartbeat couldn't stay normal, not even for a second. I AM LUCKY YES!!😭😭❤️❤️ I SO WANTED TO TELL HIM KI GAANE MEIN EK LINE HAI TV pe match khelte dekhte the , Aaj sath Chris Gayle. EK DINN HOGA TV PE BANTAI KO GAATE DEKHTE THE , AJ SATH EMIWAY KE NAACHRE HAI UNKI MUSIC VIDEO MEIN!!!! I wish and i hope ki ye bhi hojaye jald. #oneday 
CONGRATULATIONS FOR 15 MILLION SUBS BANTAI !!!!!!❤️❤️❤️
Machate raho , aag failate raho!!! 
Jamaica to India whattaa songg! Bantai with Chris Gayle - a deadly combination 😍Pura dinn yahi chalra hai bas ab toh! Vibing ayyyy💜💜
Lots of love and happiness Bantai and THANKYOU SO SO MUCH 🙏🏻🙏🏻
@emiway_bantai Rise and Shine💪🏻💕
